{"word":"G5044 - τεκνοτροφέω - teknotrophéō - tek-not-rof-eh'-o - Bring up children","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τεκνοτροφέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">teknotrophéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tek-not-rof-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring up children</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிள்ளைகளை வளர்"},{"paragraph":"to bring upchildren"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5043 - τέκνον - téknon - tek'-non/5043\">G5043</a> and <a href=\"#/G5142 - τρέφω - tréphō - tref'-o/5142\">G5142</a>; to <i>be a child rearer</i>, that is, <i>fulfil</i> the duties of <i>a female parent:</i> - bring up children.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5040/5040\">G5040</a>, <a href=\"#/G5041/5041\">G5041</a>, <a href=\"#/G5042/5042\">G5042</a>, <a href=\"#/G5043/5043\">G5043</a>, <a href=\"#/G5044/5044\">G5044</a>"}]}